  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kings_landing_map.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/4/46/Kings_landing_map.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kings_landing_map.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>1 <a href=\"/index.php/Rosby_road\" title=\"Rosby road\">Rosby road</a>, 2 <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_Gate\" title=\"Dragon Gate\">Dragon Gate</a>, 3 <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Gate\" title=\"Iron Gate\">Iron Gate</a>, 4 <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonpit\" title=\"Dragonpit\">Dragonpit</a>, 5 <a href=\"/index.php/Shae%27s_manse\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shae&#39;s manse\">Shae's manse</a>, 6 <a href=\"/index.php/Chataya%27s_brothel\" title=\"Chataya&#39;s brothel\">Chataya's brothel</a>, 7 <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Gate\" title=\"Old Gate\">Old Gate</a>, 8 <a href=\"/index.php/Flea_Bottom\" title=\"Flea Bottom\">Flea Bottom</a>, 9 <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>, 10 <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_the_Sisters\" title=\"Street of the Sisters\">Street of the Sisters</a>, 11 <a href=\"/index.php/Gate_of_the_Gods\" title=\"Gate of the Gods\">Gate of the Gods</a>, 12 <a href=\"/index.php/Cobbler%27s_Square\" title=\"Cobbler&#39;s Square\">Cobbler's Square</a>, 13 <a href=\"/index.php/Guildhall_of_the_Alchemists\" title=\"Guildhall of the Alchemists\">Guildhall of the Alchemists</a>, 14 <a href=\"/index.php/Hook\" title=\"Hook\">Hook</a>, 15 <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sept_of_Baelor\" title=\"Great Sept of Baelor\">Great Sept of Baelor</a>, <b>16 Muddy Way</b>, 17 <a href=\"/index.php/Fishmonger%27s_Square\" title=\"Fishmonger&#39;s Square\">Fishmonger's Square</a>, 18 <a href=\"/index.php/River_Gate\" title=\"River Gate\">River Gate</a>, 19 <a href=\"/index.php/Shop_of_Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Shop of Tobho Mott\">Tobho Mott's shop</a>, 20 <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_Steel\" title=\"Street of Steel\">Street of Steel</a>, 21 <a href=\"/index.php/Harbor_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Harbor of King&#39;s Landing\">harbor</a>, 22 <a href=\"/index.php/Lion_Gate\" title=\"Lion Gate\">Lion Gate</a>, 23 <a href=\"/index.php/River_Row\" title=\"River Row\">River Row</a>, 24 <a href=\"/index.php/Fish_market\" title=\"Fish market\">fish market</a>, 25 <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_grounds_(King%27s_Landing)\" title=\"Tourney grounds (King&#39;s Landing)\">tourney grounds</a>, 26 <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Gate\" title=\"King&#39;s Gate\">King's Gate</a>, 27 <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a></div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Muddy Way</b>, originally called <b>Blackwater Way</b>, is a prominent street in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Geography\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Geography</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Geography\">Geography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Muddy_Way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Geography\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Muddy Way is one of the four straight streets which starts at the unnamed great square in the center of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, the others being the <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Way\" title=\"King&#39;s Way\">King's Way</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Gods%27_Way\" title=\"Gods&#39; Way\">Gods' Way</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_the_Sisters\" title=\"Street of the Sisters\">Street of the Sisters</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_king.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_king.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The Muddy Way runs south toward <a href=\"/index.php/Fishmonger%27s_Square\" title=\"Fishmonger&#39;s Square\">Fishmonger's Square</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/River_Gate\" title=\"River Gate\">River Gate</a>, which is also called the Mud Gate, by the <a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Rush\" title=\"Blackwater Rush\">Blackwater Rush</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Hook\" title=\"Hook\">Hook</a> runs from the Muddy Way to <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_High_Hill\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s High Hill\">Aegon's High Hill</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Muddy_Way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> rapidly grew without any planning during the first century following <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>, so much so that by the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> it became a problem; the streets were close, dark and filthy. In <a href=\"/index.php/52_AC\" title=\"52 AC\">52&#160;AC</a> Jaehaerys ordered the start of works to widen, straighten the streets, and cobble them where possible. Jaehaerys also built a great central square carved out and planted with trees, with markets and arcades beneath. From this square sprung Blackwater Way, which was quickly renamed the Muddy Way by <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Muddy_Way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Muddy_Way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>On the way back to the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> from the docks, King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon's</a> party rides along the Muddy Way before arriving at the <a href=\"/index.php/Hook\" title=\"Hook\">Hook</a>, where the <a href=\"/index.php/Riots_in_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Riots in King&#39;s Landing\">riots in King's Landing</a> begin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Muddy_Way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> sees the Muddy Way crowded when he goes with <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Winesink\" title=\"Winesink\">winesink</a> where he meets with <a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Silver_Tongue\" title=\"Symon Silver Tongue\">Symon Silver Tongue</a>. Tyrion tosses to children a fistful of <a href=\"/index.php/Currency\" title=\"Currency\">coppers</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Muddy_Way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Muddy Way was crowded, but soldiers and townfolk alike made way for the Imp and his escort.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Muddy_Way&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Birth, Death, and Betrayal Under King Jaehaerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_king.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_king.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  King's Landing.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Map_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Map of King&#39;s Landing\">Map of King's Landing</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_41\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 41\">Chapter 41</a>, Tyrion IX.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 32\">Chapter 32</a>, Tyrion IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260407210339\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.034 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.055 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 570/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8899/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2920/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 843/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3145/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   41.429      1 -total\n 64.13%   26.570      1 Template:Date\n 26.17%   10.840      6 Template:Ref\n 15.47%    6.410      6 Template:Ref/core\n  6.00%    2.484      1 Template:References\n  4.77%    1.974      1 Template:Quote\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14151-0!canonical and timestamp 20260407210349 and revision id 335720\n -->\n",
